result.notes: Sightings and recordings made by staff of and visitors to the Purbeck Marine Wildlife Reserve. Details taken from the marine recording logs from the reserve centre. Where divers and walkers have made sightings recorder is entered as 'PMWR visitor'. Not all records are from the area defined as the PMWR, but have been logged at the centre by visitors.
